{"tid":472957,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解港式濕凍重未列入聯合國世界自然遺產?","createTime":"2017-11-18T17:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T01:54:11.000Z","uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2b44f1a7a9c45e84ee717dcc4eada981ba738f","tid":472957,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"啲白鬼淨係識零下幾多度凍<br />\n有幾多識欣賞港式鐵人級濕凍😷😷"},{"pid":"29a39234602ca56308f7c75e4da330056f00d8cb","tid":472957,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"今日體感溫 = 游冰河"},{"pid":"7344a4fd1d37dd586a7158f843dcb5ece249172c","tid":472957,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"英國/澳洲仲濕仲凍<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"ddf6ec85d15540b379306460215eef0199753199","tid":472957,"uid":125552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國/澳洲仲濕仲凍<br />\n點睇</blockquote><br />\n香港濕凍先係世界第一"},{"pid":"6b976e70631162510397cca536f75341fb0a7bfb","tid":472957,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英國/澳洲仲濕仲凍<br />\n點睇</blockquote><br />\n香港濕凍先係世界第一</blockquote><br />\n真"},{"pid":"5fe9002d71e90a310bb2455ac31340068c3bbc0d","tid":472957,"uid":103514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>    當空氣潮濕時會覺得較冷。這是真的嗎？</strong><br />\n<br />\n    人體對冷的感覺視乎很多因素，例如風、濕度、站在太陽下還是在陰蔽處、是否在運動中、所穿的衣服、皮膚是乾是濕等。<br />\n<br />\n    讓我們先了解身體怎樣失熱。為簡化討論，我們假設身體是乾的、裸露的、不動的、處在靜止空氣中並在陰蔽處。問題便變成：是乾空氣還是濕空氣較快令身體失熱，即是兩者哪個導熱能力較高？<br />\n<br />\n    很多人認為濕空氣比乾空氣的導熱能力高，其實這是不正確的。實驗得出圖一的結果：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/000159_359bfc3e227d600ee5464a11096696a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F000159_359bfc3e227d600ee5464a11096696a0.png&h=d6cc6c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n    上圖顯示水氣的導熱能力實際比乾空氣低很多。如果濕度（即水氣）對空氣的導熱能力有任何影響的話，它只會減低空氣的導熱能力，而不是增加。<br />\n<br />\n    所以簡單的答案是「<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">否</span></strong>」。 <br />\n<br />\nSource 香港天文台<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu06nature/ele_air_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu06nature%2Fele_air_c.htm&d=yxrIo4T3sg0dtfJjKHS33YS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=0219074e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu06nature/ele_air_c.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6dfb93ce3a9b86e123b98d21c4f150d0d869a4f3","tid":472957,"uid":37717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"港式濕熱笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}